wiki.content:
"One Way or Another (Teenage Kicks)" is a song recorded by the British boy band One Direction, released as the 2013 Comic Relief charity single on 17 February 2013. It is a medley of Blondie's "One Way or Another" (1979) and The Undertones' "Teenage Kicks" (1978).
